          <li><a href="#why-journal">Why a Decision Journal Changes Everything</a></li>
          <li><a href="#the-problem">The Problem with Learning from Experience</a></li>
          <li><a href="#what-to-record">What to Record: The Decision Journal Template</a></li>
          <li><a href="#how-to-review">How to Review: Extracting the Learning</a></li>
          <li><a href="#which-decisions">Which Decisions Belong in the Journal?</a></li>
          <li><a href="#common-mistakes">The Most Common Decision Journal Mistakes</a></li>
          <li><a href="#build-the-habit">Building the Habit: Making It Stick</a></li>
          <li><a href="#conclusion">Conclusion</a></li>
        </ol>
      </nav>

      <!-- Top Ad -->
      <div class="ad-unit ad-unit--top">
        <ins class="adsbygoogle"
             style="display:block"
             data-ad-client="ca-pub-7229511013815291"
             data-ad-slot="2952775705"
             data-ad-format="auto"
             data-full-width-responsive="true"></ins>
        <script>(adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});</script>
